PSSE raw file replaces the 3 three winding transformers with 3 two winding transformers which neglect the tertiary windings. The tertiary windings aren't  connectted to anythings. (1) In one line diagram, transformer TR83 is a three winding auto transformer. Cape replaces this three winding transformer with 2 two winding transformers,((5340,8021) and (5340,776)). 5340 is 345 kV, 8021 is 34.5kV and 776 is 34.5kV. PSSE raw replaces the three winding auto transformer with 3 two winders. (270883,275214(3M)), (275214(3M),272465), (275214(2M),275314). 270883 is 345kV, 275214 is 138kV, 272465 is 138kV and 275314 is 34.5kV.
